Moi, c'est pareil.

177
00:10:25,290 --> 00:10:26,610
Salut, Stan.

178
00:10:26,770 --> 00:10:28,290
- Salut, Chef.
- Comment ça va?

179
00:10:28,450 --> 00:10:29,440
